                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 24.) I went to Mr. Aspland's, and his wife gave me these three books.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Ellis's Defence.</hi> I was going up the town, and met Ferraway; he said he found these books in the churchyard, and if I would not have them he would throw them away.</p>
